OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman found dead in Pontypool
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a 74 year-old-man was
OL,8,Ffound dead as an address in Trevethin,
OL,9,FPontypool.
OL,11,FGwent Police officers attended a
OL,12,Fproperty on Bythway Road at around
OL,13,F4.55pm on Thursday 23 April after
OL,14,Freports that a man had received
OL,15,Fserious injuries.
OL,17,FParamedics from the Welsh Ambulance
OL,18,FService and Welsh Air Ambulance were
OL,19,Fin attendance, but he was pronounced
OL,20,Fdead at the scene.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
