OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman found dead in Pontypool
OL,6,FThe man's family has been informed and
OL,7,Fare being support by specialist
OL,8,Fofficers.
OL,10,FA 37-year-old man from Cwmbran has
OL,11,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,12,Fand is currently in police custody.
OL,14,FSenior investigating officer,
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Neil Blyth
OL,16,Fsaid:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
