OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777036266
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman found dead in Pontypool
OL,6,F"We would like to reassure the
OL,7,Fcommunities of Trevethin that we are
OL,8,Fdoing everything we can to establish
OL,9,Fthe circumstances surrounding his
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,F"We understand that reports of this
OL,13,Fnature can cause concern, however we
OL,14,Fhave arrested a man from the area who
OL,15,Fwas known to the victim, and we are
OL,16,Fnot looking for anyone else in
OL,17,Fconnection with this incident.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
