PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777036266
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman found dead in Pontypool
OL,6,F"It is important that people do not
OL,7,Fspeculate about the identities of
OL,8,Fthose involved or the circumstances
OL,9,Fsurrounding the incident as this could
OL,10,Fpresent problems to our investigation,
OL,11,Fand we encourage anyone with
OL,12,Finformation to please contact us in
OL,13,Fthe usual ways."
OL,15,FAnyone with information can contact us
OL,16,Fby calling 101, sending a direct
OL,17,Fmessage on social media quoting log
OL,18,Freference 2600125343.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
